the woman I love.


780
00:42:41.937 --> 00:42:43.188
It's better than
losing her.


781
00:42:43.272 --> 00:42:45.357
Call it a fantasy, call it a
dream, call it pretend.


782
00:42:45.440 --> 00:42:47.818
A dream might be a lie,
but it's also true.


783
00:42:47.901 --> 00:42:48.944
Wait, what?

784
00:42:49.027 --> 00:42:51.363
