<i>Fear</i>

808
00:43:51.173 --> 00:43:55.886
<i>I'd give anything</i>
<i>for someone to say</i>


809
00:43:57.512 --> 00:44:00.349
<i>All the words</i>
<i>I don't have</i>


810
00:44:00.432 --> 00:44:03.435
<i>And I can't</i>
<i>put together</i>


811
00:44:03.518 --> 00:44:09.566
<i>I'd give anything for</i>
<i>someone to say to her</i>


812
00:44:09.650 --> 00:44:13.445
<i>That she's all</i>
<i>I can think about</i>


813
00:44:13.528 --> 00:44:16.365
<i>And I can't live</i>
<i>without her</i>


814
00:44:32.297 --> 00:44:35.467
<i>My father told me</i>

815
00:44:35.550 --> 00:44:42.557
<i>Letters and books</i>
<i>weren't meant for the son of a soldier</i>


816
00:44:44.893 --> 00:44:47.646
<i>Courage and steel</i>

817
00:44:47.729 --> 00:44:52.234
<i>The trials of the
real world are what matter</i>


