<i>That they can't live</i>
<i>without me</i>


834
00:45:54.087 --> 00:45:56.840
<i>And they'll</i>
<i>be there forever</i>


835
00:45:56.924 --> 00:45:59.426
<i>I'd give anything</i>
<i>for someone to say to me</i>


836
00:46:03.096 --> 00:46:06.892
<i>That no matter</i>
<i>how bad it gets</i>


837
00:46:06.975 --> 00:46:10.812
<i>They won't</i>
<i>turn away from me</i>


838
00:46:15.817 --> 00:46:17.110
Here.

839
00:46:18.570 --> 00:46:20.572
