<i>thinking back</i>


863
00:48:29.493 --> 00:48:34.957
<i>Oh, my first sight of you</i>
<i>was my first heart attack</i>


864
00:48:35.040 --> 00:48:38.585
<i>Every letter makes me</i>
<i>lose my reason</i>


865
00:48:38.669 --> 00:48:40.087
<i>Every word is like</i>
<i>your kindest touch</i>


866
00:48:42.965 --> 00:48:46.510
<i>And if I told you</i>
<i>how much I need you</i>


867
00:48:46.593 --> 00:48:49.304
<i>Would you give me yourself</i>
<i>or turn and run?</i>


868
00:48:51.682 --> 00:48:55.519
<i>You light up desire</i>
<i>just by describing it</i>


869
00:48:55.602 --> 00:48:59.356
<i>I read to myself</i>
<i>until I go blind</i>


870
00:48:59.439 --> 00:49:03.735
<i>Your words fall around me</i>
<i>all through the night</i>


871
00:49:03.819 --> 00:49:06.905
<i>I can't resist</i>
<i>and I don't want to fight</i>


872
00:49:06.989 --> 00:49:08.782
<i>Will you be held?</i>

873
00:49:08.865 --> 00:49:10.534
<i>Will you be touched?</i>

874
00:49:10.617 --> 00:49:12.536
<i>By my hand</i>
<i>through this paper</i>


875
00:49:12.619 --> 00:49:14.746
<i>Is this all too much?</i>

876
00:49:14.830 --> 00:49:16.790
<i>Will we be ravaged?</i>

877
00:49:16.873 --> 00:49:18.583
<i>Will we be true?</i>

878
00:49:18.667 --> 00:49:22.713
<i>To somebody perfect</i>
<i>somebody like you</i>


879
00:49:22.796 --> 00:49:24.756
<i>I'm tired</i>
<i>of yearning</i>


880
00:49:24.840 --> 00:49:26.758
<i>I'm tired</i>
<i>of learning</i>


881
00:49:26.842 --> 00:49:28.719
<i>I need to drink you</i>

882
00:49:28.802 --> 00:49:30.929
<i>My heart</i>
<i>has been burning</i>


883
00:49:31.013 --> 00:49:32.848
<i>Ever since I saw you</i>

884
00:49:32.931 --> 00:49:34.933
<i>Backwards through the glass</i>

885
00:49:35.017 --> 00:49:36.768
<i>Of a thin windowpane</i>

886
00:49:36.852 --> 00:49:38.812
<i>Like a thin</i>
<i>see-through mask</i>


887
00:49:38.895 --> 00:49:40.856
<i>These words are the truth</i>

888
00:49:40.939 --> 00:49:42.482
