889
00:49:42.566 --> 00:49:45.110
<i>Through your</i>
<i>thin-fingered gloves</i>


890
00:49:45.193 --> 00:49:46.945
<i>To your hand, to your skin</i>

891
00:49:47.029 --> 00:49:48.947
<i>Like ribbons on wrist</i>

892
00:49:49.031 --> 00:49:50.949
<i>Let them hold you</i>
<i>and twist</i>


893
00:49:51.033 --> 00:49:53.201
<i>Let them</i>
