yours, just differently put.


944
00:52:28.690 --> 00:52:30.734
But both are
endlessly quotable.


945
00:52:30.817 --> 00:52:32.069
You know his letters
by heart?


946
00:52:35.530 --> 00:52:36.531
Every one.

947
00:52:40.535 --> 00:52:42.454
You will arrange
the meeting?


948
00:52:42.537 --> 00:52:45.707
As ever,
I am at your service.


949
00:52:54.549 --> 00:52:56.176
I've come
to say goodbye.


950
00:52:56.260 --> 00:52:58.720
I leave tonight
for the front.


951
00:52:58.804 --> 00:53:00.681
It's grim,
but orders are orders.


952
00:53:01.848 --> 00:53:03.558
We're losing the war.

953
00:53:03.642 --> 00:53:06.353
