00:54:05.996 --> 00:54:10.417
Why don't you leave him
and all the guards behind?


977
00:54:10.500 --> 00:54:13.712
Here in the city
with the women and children.


978
00:54:13.795 --> 00:54:15.631
Oh, he'll hate that.

979
00:54:15.714 --> 00:54:18.884
More than hate,
it would humiliate him.


980
00:54:18.967 --> 00:54:21.887
No heroics, no medals.

981
00:54:21.970 --> 00:54:24.640
His warrior pride
is his great weakness.


982
00:54:24.723 --> 00:54:29.436
Am I to understand
this as an act of love?


983
00:54:31.355 --> 00:54:32.481
It is.

984
00:54:34.816 --> 00:54:38.278
I hereby bury his orders
to the front.


985
00:54:39.947 --> 00:54:41.740
Poor little Cyrano...

986
00:54:41.823 --> 00:54:43.450
and his
poor little friends.


987
00:54:47.329 --> 00:54:49.456
Marie, some tea.

988
00:54:52.292 --> 00:54:54.211
I'm afraid we are
out of tea, sir.


989
00:54:54.294 --> 00:54:55.671
Leave us.

990
00:55:06.598 --> 00:55:09.476
I like your tricks.

991
00:55:11.603 --> 00:55:13.397
I wager
you know some more.


992
00:55:13.981 --> 00:55:15.065
No, sir.

993
00:55:15.148 --> 00:55:16.608
Oh, I think you do.

994
00:55:16.692 --> 00:55:18.527
How can I leave you?

995
00:55:19.695 --> 00:55:21.196
Maybe I won't.

996
00:55:22.155 --> 00:55:23.490
Roxanne...

997
00:55:25.867 --> 00:55:27.619
I love you.

998
00:55:27.703 --> 00:55:29.162
I love you.

999
00:55:30.706 --> 00:55:32.958
It's a terrible shame,
but leave you must.


1000
00:55:33.041 --> 00:55:34.960
The battle
can't happen...


1001
00:55:35.043 --> 00:55:36.253
without the colonel.

1002
00:55:39.506 --> 00:55:41.508
I so admire
your bravery.


1003
00:55:41.592 --> 00:55:42.801
Yeah, I'm not brave.

1004
00:55:42.884 --> 00:55:45.095
I'm dutiful.
You are too modest.


1005
00:55:45.178 --> 00:55:47.598
It is you who will lead
the charge into battle.


1006
00:55:49.349 --> 00:55:52.686
I could not love a man
who hides from danger.


1007
00:55:52.769 --> 00:55:54.563
Do you love me?

1008
00:55:56.189 --> 00:55:58.609
I love the man
for whom I fear.


1009
00:56:01.069 --> 00:56:03.447
So I must go to war?

1010
00:56:06.825 --> 00:56:07.826
Yes.

1011
00:56:23.258 --> 00:56:24.843
This is folly.

1012
00:56:24.927 --> 00:56:26.595
She said she wants to meet me,
so what's wrong with surprising her?


1013
00:56:26.678 --> 00:56:27.804
You're not prepared.

1014
00:56:27.888 --> 00:56:29.014
She loves me,
I don't need to prepare.


1015
00:56:29.097 --> 00:56:30.766
Why can't you relax?

1016
00:56:30.849 --> 00:56:32.309
Can you at least take a look at
these conversational witticisms?


1017
00:56:32.392 --> 00:56:33.477
No, thank you.

1018
00:56:33.560 --> 00:56:34.770
Memorize this now!

1019
00:56:34.853 --> 00:56:36.313
I'm going to
speak to her in my own words.


1020
00:56:36.396 --> 00:56:38.565
I strongly advise
against that.


1021
00:56:38.649 --> 00:56:40.692
And when the moment is right,
I'll take her in my arms.


1022
00:56:40.776 --> 00:56:43.195
There will be no moment
if you don't study these.


1023
00:56:43.278 --> 00:56:44.780
I'll be fine.

1024
00:56:44.863 --> 00:56:47.032
All your fancy words and phrases
are now a part of my vocabulary.


1025
00:56:47.115 --> 00:56:48.700
I'll simply repeat them.

1026
00:56:48.784 --> 00:56:49.868
No, wait, what is it?

1027
00:56:49.952 --> 00:56:51.036
Regurgitate?

1028
00:56:51.119 --> 00:56:52.788
That's it!
That's what I will do.


1029
00:56:53.580 --> 00:56:54.957
Off you go then.

1030
00:57:05.300 --> 00:57:08.720
I'm very grateful
for your help...


1031
00:57:08.804 --> 00:57:11.473
but, with extreme respect, I
don't think I need you anymore.


1032
00:57:12.057 --> 00:57:13.058
Very well.

1033
00:57:14.893 --> 00:57:16.603
Fly to Roxanne.

1034
00:57:16.687 --> 00:57:19.439
Dazzle her with your
transcendent words.


1035
00:57:22.859 --> 00:57:23.860
Yeah.

1036
00:57:34.830 --> 00:57:36.248
WO Can you imagine?

1037
00:57:37.457 --> 00:57:38.709
Champagne!

1038
00:58:03.859 --> 00:58:06.403
- <i>"We don't write poems</i>
-<i>to be happy.</i>


1039
00:58:06.486 --> 00:58:08.405
"We write
to discover meaning.


1040
00:58:08.488 --> 00:58:12.409
"We write to revenge loss
and explicate love...


1041
00:58:12.492 --> 00:58:14.286
"to miss nothing in the profound
hope that upon our deaths...


1042
00:58:16.663 --> 00:58:17.956
"we continue...

1043
00:58:21.668 --> 00:58:24.963
"to live in the words."

1044
00:58:32.888 --> 00:58:34.389
Christian.

1045
00:58:36.058 --> 00:58:37.225
Hello.

1046
00:58:38.310 --> 00:58:40.103
How did you know
I was here?


1047
00:58:40.187 --> 00:58:44.483
Which is not to say that I
flatter myself by thinking you are here to see me.


1048
00:58:44.566 --> 00:58:45.817
I heard about this...

1049
00:58:45.901 --> 00:58:47.069
Women's-only salon?

1050
00:58:49.237 --> 00:58:51.239
Yes. From a friend.

1051
00:58:52.157 --> 00:58:53.283
Is she here?

1052
00:58:53.367 --> 00:58:54.493
No, she's a man.

1053
00:58:54.576 --> 00:58:55.994
I mean, he is.

1054
00:58:59.247 --> 00:59:01.166
Will you come with me?

1055
00:59:01.249 --> 00:59:02.751
So we can talk?

1056
00:59:05.170 --> 00:59:06.421
Of course.

1057
00:59:13.428 --> 00:59:14.763
Isn't it beautiful?

1058
00:59:19.434 --> 00:59:21.353
Do you suffer
from vertigo?


1059
00:59:21.436 --> 00:59:23.272
No. But I don't
like heights.


1060
00:59:44.626 --> 00:59:48.046
There are some silences
that are comfortable...


1061
00:59:48.130 --> 00:59:51.717
and then there are some
that are freighted with tension.


1062
00:59:51.800 --> 00:59:54.386
What do you think
the nature of this one is?


1063
00:59:58.015 --> 01:00:01.560
I think it's
a bit of both.


1064
01:00:02.477 --> 01:00:03.562
I agree.

1065
01:00:10.319 --> 01:00:11.486
Talk to me.

1066
01:00:13.655 --> 01:00:14.740
I love you.

1067
01:00:14.823 --> 01:00:15.866
Yes.

1068
01:00:17.868 --> 01:00:24.958
Sometimes raw, simple words are
the most potent deployment of language.


1069
01:00:25.042 --> 01:00:26.126
I love you.

1070
01:00:26.209 --> 01:00:29.004
The sheer surprise
of repetition.


1071
01:00:29.755 --> 01:00:31.673
But say some more.

1072
01:00:31.757 --> 01:00:32.883
What else?

1073
01:00:34.343 --> 01:00:36.345
I love you so much.

1074
01:00:40.057 --> 01:00:42.809
When you write, you say it in a
thousand different ways...


1075
01:00:42.893 --> 01:00:48.440
without ever resorting to those
three overused little words.


1076
01:00:48.523 --> 01:00:50.275
Which little words?

1077
01:00:50.359 --> 01:00:54.279
Please,
my dearest Christian...


1078
01:00:54.363 --> 01:00:57.866
speak to me
like you do in your letters.


1079
01:01:01.787 --> 01:01:05.457
You are an angel
to be adored.


1080
01:01:06.792 --> 01:01:10.045
My love is
so, so big...


1081
01:01:12.422 --> 01:01:14.299
it is absord.

1082
01:01:14.383 --> 01:01:16.176
I'm sorry?

1083
01:01:16.260 --> 01:01:18.220
You are
a beautiful flower.


1084
01:01:19.721 --> 01:01:21.265
May I smell your neck?

1085
01:01:22.391 --> 01:01:26.561
Or give it a peck
at this violet hour?


1086
01:01:26.645 --> 01:01:29.147
Neuvillette, sir.

1087
01:01:29.231 --> 01:01:30.315
Don't go!
Please wait.


1088
01:01:30.399 --> 01:01:31.650
My passion has
rendered me...


1089
01:01:31.733 --> 01:01:32.943
What is it?
Stupid?


1090
01:01:33.026 --> 01:01:34.194
No, but it does
begin with an "S."


1091
01:01:34.278 --> 01:01:36.113
Let me know when
you've found it.


1092
01:01:37.030 --> 01:01:39.283
And I am not a flower.

1093
01:01:39.908 --> 01:01:41.034
I need more.

1094
01:01:41.118 --> 01:01:42.494
I need more.

1095
01:01:42.577 --> 01:01:43.745
I need more.

1096
01:01:49.584 --> 01:01:53.505
<i>I need more</i>

1097
01:01:53.588 --> 01:01:55.632
<i>I need more</i>
<i>I need more</i>


1098
01:01:55.716 --> 01:02:00.512
<i>Don't you dare</i>
<i>tell me you love me</i>


1099
01:02:00.596 --> 01:02:04.433
<i>I've heard that line before</i>

1100
01:02:05.684 --> 01:02:06.852
Speechless!

1101
01:02:06.935 --> 01:02:08.437
That's the word.

1102
01:02:16.278 --> 01:02:17.529
That went well.

1103
01:02:17.613 --> 01:02:18.989
You spied on us?

1104
01:02:20.282 --> 01:02:22.075
I couldn't resist.

1105
01:02:22.951 --> 01:02:24.077
Help me.

1106
01:02:24.161 --> 01:02:25.704
Please.

1107
01:02:25.787 --> 01:02:27.331
No.

1108
01:02:28.165 --> 01:02:31.251
You don't need me.

1109
01:02:31.335 --> 01:02:35.088
<i>Talk of the blank space</i>
<i>behind the sun</i>


1110
01:02:35.172 --> 01:02:36.548
<i>Where you told me</i>
<i>you'd meet me when everyone's gone</i>


1111
01:02:39.176 --> 01:02:42.054
<i>Tell me that</i>
<i>nothing makes sense</i>


1112
01:02:42.137 --> 01:02:44.890
<i>But the sound of my voice</i>
<i>in your head</i>


1113
01:02:44.973 --> 01:02:48.101
<i>Even when</i>
<i>I'm nowhere around</i>


1114
01:02:48.185 --> 01:02:52.564
<i>Make love make sense</i>
<i>in the loveliest way</i>


1115
01:02:52.648 --> 01:02:56.568
<i>Infinite and simple</i>
<i>in an ink black sky</i>


1116
01:02:56.652 --> 01:03:00.572
<i>Turn me to water</i>
<i>like your letters do</i>


1117
01:03:00.656 --> 01:03:04.743
<i>Make me not know</i>
<i>whether to laugh or cry</i>


1118
01:03:04.826 --> 01:03:08.872
<i>I need more</i>

1119
01:03:08.956 --> 01:03:10.832
<i>I need more</i>

1120
01:03:10.916 --> 01:03:15.754
<i>I need waves of desire</i>
<i>to come over me</i>


1121
01:03:15.837 --> 01:03:19.925
<i>And teardrops</i>
<i>on the floor</i>


1122
01:03:20.008 --> 01:03:24.930
-<i>I feel like I've
been too long</i> -<i>with my thoughts anyway</i>


1123
01:03:25.013 --> 01:03:28.767
<i>I've cornered myself</i>
<i>in the loneliest place</i>


1124
01:03:28.850 --> 01:03:33.105
<i>I won't let you lose me</i>
<i>now that you've found me</i>


1125
01:03:33.188 --> 01:03:37.109
<i>You know what to say</i>
<i>so just say it now to me</i>


1126
01:03:37.192 --> 01:03:40.946
<i>I float through the hours</i>
<i>with everyone else</i>


1127
01:03:41.029 --> 01:03:45.242
<i>But I always only</i>
<i>think of you by myself</i>


1128
01:03:45.325 --> 01:03:48.078
<i>Tell me your secrets</i>
<i>Who are you in private?</i>


1129
01:03:48.161 --> 01:03:49.621
Oh.

1130
01:03:49.705 --> 01:03:53.709
<i>When you can't sleep</i>
<i>tell me how you survive it</i>


1131
01:03:53.792 --> 01:03:57.671
<i>I need more</i>

1132
01:03:57.754 --> 01:03:59.673
<i>I need more</i>

1133
01:03:59.756 --> 01:04:04.678
<i>I need waves of desire</i>
<i>to come over me</i>


1134
01:04:04.761 --> 01:04:07.889
<i>And teardrops</i>
<i>on the floor</i>


1135
01:04:07.973 --> 01:04:09.266
Help me. I beg you.

1136
01:04:09.349 --> 01:04:10.934
If I don't win her back,
I'll die.


1137
01:04:11.018 --> 01:04:13.186
Then you'd better
improve your regurgitation skills.


1138
01:04:13.270 --> 01:04:15.647
All right,
I need you.


1139
01:04:15.731 --> 01:04:18.066
I was an idiot to believe I
didn't. I apologize.


1140
01:04:18.150 --> 01:04:19.818
You need me?
Always.


1141
01:04:19.901 --> 01:04:21.737
Am I essential?
Of course.


1142
01:04:21.820 --> 01:04:23.655
Will you say my words without
pedantry, prevarication, or quibbling?


1143
01:04:27.618 --> 01:04:28.702
Just say yes.

1144
01:04:28.785 --> 01:04:29.911
Yes.

1145
01:04:29.995 --> 01:04:31.455
Good. Follow me.

1146
01:04:32.414 --> 01:04:36.501
<i>I need more</i>

1147
01:04:36.585 --> 01:04:38.211
<i>I need more</i>

1148
01:04:38.295 --> 01:04:43.508
<i>Don't you dare tell me</i>
<i>you love me</i>


1149
01:04:43.592 --> 01:04:47.387
<i>I've heard that line before</i>

1150
01:04:47.471 --> 01:04:50.933
<i>I've heard that line before</i>

1151
01:04:51.016 --> 01:04:53.685
<i>I need more</i>

1152
01:04:53.769 --> 01:04:55.103
Right. Now, you stand there.

1153
01:04:55.812 --> 01:04:57.439
And I will be here.

1154
01:04:57.522 --> 01:04:59.566
And when she returns, I will
whisper what you must say to her.


1155
01:04:59.650 --> 01:05:01.234
No.

1156
01:05:01.318 --> 01:05:03.570
Yes.
I will feed you the words.


1157
01:05:03.654 --> 01:05:05.614
It's madness!
How can it possibly work?


1158
01:05:08.450 --> 01:05:10.619
Do not
ruin this again.


1159
01:05:24.508 --> 01:05:25.884
Roxanne.

1160
01:05:25.968 --> 01:05:27.469
Roxanne.

1161
01:05:32.808 --> 01:05:33.976
Who's there?

1162
01:05:34.059 --> 01:05:35.602
Speechless Christian.

1163
01:05:35.686 --> 01:05:37.354
I must talk to you.

1164
01:05:37.437 --> 01:05:39.731
I'd rather
read your letters.


1165
01:05:39.815 --> 01:05:41.400
Please.

1166
01:05:41.483 --> 01:05:44.278
Do you regret
what happened this evening?


1167
01:05:44.361 --> 01:05:45.821
Yes.

1168
01:05:46.154 --> 01:05:47.364
Yes?

1169
01:05:49.324 --> 01:05:52.077
That's your considered
explanation and apology?


1170
01:05:52.160 --> 01:05:54.579
I'm beginning to fear
you're just a weird young man...


1171
01:05:54.663 --> 01:05:56.915
who likes writing letters.

1172
01:05:56.999 --> 01:05:58.542
Maybe you don't even
love me.


1173
01:05:59.543 --> 01:06:01.003
Good night.

1174
01:06:02.254 --> 01:06:03.297
Wait.

1175
01:06:05.882 --> 01:06:07.467
I could no more
stop loving you...


1176
01:06:07.551 --> 01:06:09.595
I could no more
stop loving you...


1177
01:06:09.678 --> 01:06:11.388
...than I could
stop the sun rising.


1178
01:06:11.471 --> 01:06:13.265
...than I can
stop the sun rising.


1179
01:06:13.849 --> 01:06:16.184
Really?

1180
01:06:16.268 --> 01:06:19.938
My cruel love has never stopped
growing in my soul...


1181
01:06:20.022 --> 01:06:21.773
From the day
it was born there.


1182
01:06:21.857 --> 01:06:23.191
...from the day
it was born.


1183
01:06:24.318 --> 01:06:25.902
There.
There.


1184
01:06:27.195 --> 01:06:30.616
If your love is cruel,
you should have killed it.


1185
01:06:30.699 --> 01:06:32.367
I tried.

1186
01:06:32.451 --> 01:06:35.829
-It has the strength of Hercules. I tried.
-It has the strength of...


1187
01:06:35.912 --> 01:06:37.039
Hercules.

1188
01:06:37.122 --> 01:06:38.624
...Hercules.

1189
01:06:38.707 --> 01:06:39.750
Got anything better?

1190
01:06:41.126 --> 01:06:44.463
Do continue. Please.

1191
01:06:44.546 --> 01:06:47.132
Roxanne, my love for you
is so powerful...


1192
01:06:47.215 --> 01:06:50.802
Roxanne, my love for you
is so powerful...


1193
01:06:50.886 --> 01:06:52.471
...it has strangled
the two serpents...


1194
01:06:52.554 --> 01:06:54.681
...it has strangled
the two serpents...


1195
01:06:55.724 --> 01:06:57.059
pride and doubt.

1196
01:06:59.728 --> 01:07:01.229
Why do you speak
so haltingly?


1197
01:07:02.773 --> 01:07:03.982
This is impossible.

1198
01:07:04.066 --> 01:07:05.442
No, it's working,
keep going.


1199
01:07:05.525 --> 01:07:07.402
Are you going to
answer my question?


1200
01:07:11.323 --> 01:07:13.408
My speech seems halting...

1201
01:07:13.492 --> 01:07:18.163
because in this darkness my
words must stumble to your ear.


1202
01:07:18.246 --> 01:07:19.498
What are you doing?

1203
01:07:19.581 --> 01:07:21.833
My words have no such
difficulty.


1204
01:07:21.917 --> 01:07:24.002
Your words fall,
mine must climb.


1205
01:07:24.086 --> 01:07:27.172
Then perhaps
I should come down to you.


1206
01:07:27.255 --> 01:07:28.340
No.
No.


1207
01:07:30.634 --> 01:07:32.844
Why not?

1208
01:07:32.928 --> 01:07:35.472
I like this way
of talking.


1209
01:07:35.555 --> 01:07:37.724
I like being invisible
to each other.


1210
01:07:39.393 --> 01:07:43.563
I cannot be stunned into silence
by your beauty.


1211
01:07:43.647 --> 01:07:48.277
Here in this awkwardness, I am
free at last to speak from my heart.


1212
01:07:49.278 --> 01:07:51.363
Why is your voice
an octave lower?


1213
01:07:55.450 --> 01:07:57.369
I'm daring
to be myself.


1214
01:08:00.163 --> 01:08:03.166
Why would you fear
to be yourself?


1215
01:08:04.126 --> 01:08:05.127
To be laughed at.

1216
01:08:05.752 --> 01:08:07.004
For what?

1217
01:08:09.840 --> 01:08:11.925
For having
too much emotion.


1218
01:08:12.009 --> 01:08:13.010
I do not look...

1219
01:08:14.303 --> 01:08:16.179
Speak as I feel.

1220
01:08:17.639 --> 01:08:19.641
<i>The way I feel is like</i>

1221
01:08:21.643 --> 01:08:24.938
<i>Falling stars</i>

1222
01:08:25.022 --> 01:08:31.236
<i>Diving into</i>
<i>cold ocean waves</i>


1223
01:08:31.320 --> 01:08:37.576
