<i>how much I need you</i>


1230
01:09:03.352 --> 01:09:06.688
<i>But I turn and run</i>

1231
01:09:09.983 --> 01:09:16.114
<i>Your letters to me</i>
<i>are like music</i>


1232
01:09:16.198 --> 01:09:22.120
<i>They're just a mask in a</i>
<i>lonely coward's game</i>


1233
01:09:22.204 --> 01:09:28.752
<i>What is it</i>
<i>you're so afraid of losing?</i>


1234
01:09:28.835 --> 01:09:36.134
