1825
01:51:56.925 --> 01:51:59.595
<i>It's okay, Roxanne</i>

1826
01:51:59.678 --> 01:52:02.347
<i>I've known what I am</i>

1827
01:52:02.431 --> 01:52:06.935
<i>From the second</i>
<i>your eyes held mine</i>


1828
01:52:09.229 --> 01:52:11.273
<i>Ever since then</i>

1829
01:52:11.356 --> 01:52:14.526
<i>I've been a patient man</i>

1830
01:52:15.319 --> 01:52:19.448
<i>Patient with desire</i>

1831
01:52:21.074 --> 01:52:23.869
<i>I know, Cyrano</i>

1832
01:52:23.952 --> 01:52:27.164
<i>I know who you are</i>

1833
01:52:27.247 --> 01:52:31.335
<i>Love, I feel the same</i>

1834
01:52:33.086 --> 01:52:35.839
<i>So, no, Cyrano</i>

1835
01:52:35.922 --> 01:52:38.884
<i>I won't let you go</i>

1836
01:52:38.967 --> 01:52:44.014
<i>Love's a painful</i>
<i>painful game</i>


1837
01:52:45.807 --> 01:52:47.267
You love me.

1838
01:52:48.352 --> 01:52:49.353
Yes.

1839
01:52:50.270 --> 01:52:52.564
And I will not
lose you twice.


